text: Madlaina Matter (born 19 October 1996) is a Swiss female volleyball player. She played at the 2016 Montreux Volley Masters, 2017 Montreux Volley Masters, 2018 Montreux Volley Masters, 2019 Montreux Volley Masters, and 2019 Women's European Volleyball Championship. She played for Sm'Aesch Pfeffingen. == References == Category:1996 births Category:Swiss volleyball players Category:Living people
